# shadcn/ui & TanStack — Never Edit

**Never modify generated or framework-primitive files.**

## shadcn/ui (`frontend/src/components/ui/`)
Components installed via `npx shadcn@latest add`. Edits get wiped on reinstall.

Custom styling goes in:
- `globals.css` (global CSS, `@theme` tokens)
- `className` props on usage sites
- Wrapper components in `frontend/src/components/app/`

## TanStack Router (`frontend/src/routeTree.gen.ts`)
Auto-generated by `@tanstack/react-router` codegen (`tsr generate`). Manual edits are overwritten on the next codegen run.

Route definitions live in the source route files under `frontend/src/routes/`.
